.co.jp/inquiry\">お問い合わせ</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </nav>\n        <div class=\"otoiawase-area\">\n          <p class=\"tel\"><img src=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/images/common/ico_freedial.png\" width=\"21\" height=\"14\" alt=\"フリーダイヤル\">0120-79-5520</p>\n          <p class=\"btn-inq\"><a href=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/inquiry\">お問い合わせ</a></p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"tel visible-xs\"><img src=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/images/common/ico_freedial.png\" width=\"21\" height=\"14\" alt=\"フリーダイヤル\"><a href=\"tel:0120795520\">0120-79-5520</a></p>\n  </header><!-- header-area-wrap--><!-- #EndLibraryItem -->\n<div class=\"contents-area bg-news\">\n    <p class=\"page-title\">新着情報</p>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"breadcrumb\">\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/\"> ホーム</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp//news\"> 新着情報</a></li>\n  <li>山林建設工事部の業務紹介</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"contents\">\n  <div class=\"row\">\n    <div class=\"col-sm-9\">\n        <section class=\"news-area clearfix\">\n          <div class=\"info-list\">\n            <div class=\"title-area\">\n              <h1 class=\"title-02\">山林建設工事部の業務紹介</h1>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"detail-date\">\n              <time datetime=\"2022-07-11\">2022年7月11日</time>\n              <span class=\"label cat-info\">通信</span>\n            </p>\n                          <div class=\"cms-area icon clearfix\">\n                <p>山林建設工事部の業務風景などをご紹介！</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">・教育</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">未経験者でも指導の元、確かな技術を身に着けていきます。</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">□伐採指導</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1614\" src=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/4287896d9e597ce85b4618f544d286e5-239x320.jpg\" alt=\"穴水現場　伐採指導\" width=\"239\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/4287896d9e597ce85b4618f544d286e5-239x320.jpg 239w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/4287896d9e597ce85b4618f544d286e5.jpg 449w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 239px) 100vw, 239px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">□下草刈り安全指導</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1622\" src=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/7.13-320x241.jpg\" alt=\"7.13\" width=\"320\" height=\"241\" srcset=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/7.13-320x241.jpg 320w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/7.13-768x578.jpg 768w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/7.13-670x504.jpg 670w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/7.13.jpg 797w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">・作業例</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">□下草刈り</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1605\" src=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/S__43712519-239x320.jpg\" alt=\"S__43712519\" width=\"239\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/S__43712519-239x320.jpg 239w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/S__43712519.jpg 449w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 239px) 100vw, 239px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">□枝打ち</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1601\" src=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/2239-240x320.jpg\" alt=\"2239\" width=\"240\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/2239-240x320.jpg 240w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/2239.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">□伐採</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1602\" src=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/1579-240x320.jpg\" alt=\"1579\" width=\"240\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/1579-240x320.jpg 240w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/1579.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">□シイの木の伐採</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1606\" src=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/39de3bb3d9292eaa80d8ea661f8895e8-240x320.jpg\" alt=\"掛川市　ｿｰﾗｰ現場\" width=\"240\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/39de3bb3d9292eaa80d8ea661f8895e8-240x320.jpg 240w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/39de3bb3d9292eaa80d8ea661f8895e8.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">□簡易架線</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">スイングヤーダで簡易架線を張り、材木を収集</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1616\" src=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/20210324_111818-e1657502217789-240x320.jpg\" alt=\"20210324_111818\" width=\"240\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/20210324_111818-e1657502217789-240x320.jpg 240w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/20210324_111818-e1657502217789-503x670.jpg 503w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/20210324_111818-e1657502217789.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">□フェラバンチャ(伐倒機械)</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">伐倒や道作りもこの1台で行えます。</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1617\" src=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/IMG_4312-240x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_4312\" width=\"240\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/IMG_4312-240x320.jpg 240w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/IMG_4312.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">・その他</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">□しっかり休憩。</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">暑い中でも空調服を着用して仕事をしています。</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1607\" src=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/2660-240x320.jpg\" alt=\"2660\" width=\"240\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/2660-240x320.jpg 240w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/2660.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">□集合写真</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">和気あいあいと活動中！</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1603\" src=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/S__10313742-320x240.jpg\" alt=\"S__10313742\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" srcset=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/S__10313742-320x240.jpg 320w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/S__10313742-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/S__10313742-670x503.jpg 670w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/S__10313742.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1599\" src=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/IMG_4057-320x241.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_4057\" width=\"320\" height=\"241\" srcset=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/IMG_4057-320x241.jpg 320w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/IMG_4057-768x578.jpg 768w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/IMG_4057-670x504.jpg 670w, https://www.chumoku.co.jp/wp-content/uploads/IMG_4057.jpg 797w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" /> </p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n              </div>\n                      </div>\n        </section>\n  </div><!-- main -->\n  \n  <!-- sub -->\n  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\n          <aside class=\"side-area\">\n        <h2 class=\"side-title\">カテゴリー</h2>\n          <ul>\n              <li><a href=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/news/\">すべて</a></li>\n<li class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/category/news/\" >お知らせ</a></li>\n<li class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/category/event/\" >イベント</a></li>\n<li class=\"","finalUrl":"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/info/%e5%b1%b1%e6%9e%97%e5%bb%ba%e8%a8%ad%e5%b7%a5%e4%ba%8b%e9%83%a8%e3%81%ae%e6%a5%ad%e5%8b%99%e7%b4%b9%e4%bb%8b/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-23T21:14:17.998Z"}